         <t:div xml:lang="gez" type="edition">
            <t:note>The incipit and explicit are taken from <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/TDIDAWT4"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Weischer1993QerellosII"/><title level="m">Qērellos II: Der Prosphonetikos Über den rechten Glauben des Kyrillos von Alexandrien an Arkadia und Marina, Teil 1: Einleitung mit christologischem Florilegium</title><title level="s">Äthiopistische Forschungen</title><author><forename>Bernd Manuel</forename><surname>Weischer</surname></author><pubPlace>Stuttgart</pubPlace><publisher>Franz Steiner Verlag GMBH</publisher><date>1993</date><series><title level="s">Äthiopistische Forschungen</title><biblScope unit="volume">31</biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">31</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Weischer1993QerellosII</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Weischer1993QerellosII</note></t:bibl>.</t:note>
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
               <t:ab xml:lang="gez">ሥነ፡ ዜና፡ ዘለዓለም፡ ወምክሕ፡ ዘቅዱሳት፡ አብያተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ዘመድኅነ፡ ኵልነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡
                  ለይስምዮ፡ ኵሉ፡ ሰብእ፡ በአማን፡ ኪያክን፡ ቅዱሳት፡ ወንጹሓት፡ መረዕዊሁ፡ አርቃዲያ፡ ወማሪና፡ ክልኤ፡ አኃት፡ ክቡረት፡
                  ወመፍቀርያተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘበላዕሌሆን፡ ያንጸበርቅ፡ ብዑድ፡ ስነ፡ ላሕይ። </t:ab>
            </t:div>
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="explicit">
               <t:ab xml:lang="gez">እስመ፡ በከመ፡ ውእቱ፡ ፍጹም፡ በመለኮቱ፡ ዘእምእግዚአብሔር፡ አብ፡ ቃል፡ ከማሁ፡ ፍጹም፡ በሥጋ፡ ከመ፡
                  ሰብእ፡ ዘአኮ፡ ሥጋ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ነፍስ፡ ነሥአ፡ አላ፡ ዘቦቱ፡ እንከ፡ ነፍሰ፡ ተናጋሪተ። እግዚአብሔር፡ እንከ፡ አምላከ፡ ኵሉ፡
                  ዘይሁብ፡ ለኵሎሙ፡ ለእለ፡ ይፈርህዎ፡ በረከተ፡ ዘእምሰማያት፡ ያጸግብ፡ ነፍሳቲክን፡ ቅዱሳተ፡ በጸጋ፡ ዘእምኀቤሁ፡ ከመ፡ ብጹሐ፡
                  አምጣን፡ በጺሐክን፡ በፍጻሜሁ፡ ለክርስቶስ፡ በተድለ፡ ወመዊእ፡ ዘኢይተረጐም፡ ያስተርኢ፡ ሕይወትክን፡ ቅዱሳት፡ መራዕወ፡ ንጉሥ።
               </t:ab>
            </t:div>
